{"doc_id": "97bcd2267168ef90faad7e5ab0c441d815f1402fd242f5b9e2ba2d6823f1df61", "date": "2008", "jurisdiction": "India", "year": "2008", "title": "2008_10_176_189_EN", "id": "supreme_court_judgements_2008_2008_10_176_189_en_1", "chunk_id": "supreme_court_judgements_2008_2008_10_176_189_en_1", "original_source_path": "app/Supreme_Court_Judgements/2008/2008_10_176_189_EN.json", "text": "ARIJIT PASAYAT, P. SATHASIVAM AND AFTAB ALAM, JJ~] c Uttar Pradesh Krishi Utpadan Mandi Adhiniyam, 1964 s. 17(iii)(b), Explanation appended thereto Market fee Levy of _Held: Physical presence of agricultural produce within market area is necessary for levy of mprket fee On facts, transaction of sale of the rice exported by Respondent No. 1 ~ 'D · did not take place within the market area of Appellant-Mandi ~r Samiti -: .Hence, Appellant-Mandi Samiti was not entitled to levy market fee. The question which arose for consideration in the present appeal is whether the transaction of sale of the E rice exported by· Respondent No.1 took place within the market area of the Appellant-Mandi Samiti and ther-efore the Appellant was entitled to levy market fee under s.17(iii)(b) of the Uttar Pradesh Krishi Utpadan Mandi Adhiniyam, 1964. ..._.", "start_char": 150, "end_char": 992, "num_sentences": 3, "doc_similarity": 0.0, "avg_similarity": 0.5473, "role": "Preamble", "confidence": 0.9968708157539368, "same_role_chunk_ids": ["supreme_court_judgements_2008_2008_10_176_189_en_2", "supreme_court_judgements_2008_2008_10_176_189_en_5", "supreme_court_judgements_2008_2008_10_176_189_en_6", "supreme_court_judgements_2008_2008_10_176_189_en_7", "supreme_court_judgements_2008_2008_10_176_189_en_9", "supreme_court_judgements_2008_2008_10_176_189_en_10", "supreme_court_judgements_2008_2008_10_176_189_en_11", "supreme_court_judgements_2008_2008_10_176_189_en_13", "supreme_court_judgements_2008_2008_10_176_189_en_45"]}
{"doc_id": "97bcd2267168ef90faad7e5ab0c441d815f1402fd242f5b9e2ba2d6823f1df61", "date": "2008", "jurisdiction": "India", "year": "2008", "title": "2008_10_176_189_EN", "id": "supreme_court_judgements_2008_2008_10_176_189_en_2", "chunk_id": "supreme_court_judgements_2008_2008_10_176_189_en_2", "original_source_path": "app/Supreme_Court_Judgements/2008/2008_10_176_189_EN.json", "text": "Dismissing the appeal, the Court HELD:1.1. A plain reading of s.17(iii)(b) of the Uttar Pradesh Krishi Utpadan Mandi Adhiniyam, 1964 (Act) shows that the Committee is empowered to levy and colG lect market fee which shall be payable on transaction of sale of agricultural produce in the market area. The words \"specified agricultural produce in the market area\" have great relevance.", "start_char": 993, "end_char": 1376, "num_sentences": 3, "doc_similarity": 0.0, "avg_similarity": 0.2646, "role": "Preamble", "confidence": 0.9674996733665466, "same_role_chunk_ids": ["supreme_court_judgements_2008_2008_10_176_189_en_1", "supreme_court_judgements_2008_2008_10_176_189_en_5", "supreme_court_judgements_2008_2008_10_176_189_en_6", "supreme_court_judgements_2008_2008_10_176_189_en_7", "supreme_court_judgements_2008_2008_10_176_189_en_9", "supreme_court_judgements_2008_2008_10_176_189_en_10", "supreme_court_judgements_2008_2008_10_176_189_en_11", "supreme_court_judgements_2008_2008_10_176_189_en_13", "supreme_court_judgements_2008_2008_10_176_189_en_45"]}
{"doc_id": "97bcd2267168ef90faad7e5ab0c441d815f1402fd242f5b9e2ba2d6823f1df61", "date": "2008", "jurisdiction": "India", "year": "2008", "title": "2008_10_176_189_EN", "id": "supreme_court_judgements_2008_2008_10_176_189_en_3", "chunk_id": "supreme_court_judgements_2008_2008_10_176_189_en_3", "original_source_path": "app/Supreme_Court_Judgements/2008/2008_10_176_189_EN.json", "text": "The manner of realization of market fee has been enumerated in sub clauses (1 ), (2), (3) & (4) of H 176 KRISHI UTPADAN MANDI SAMIT!, GHAZIABAD v. 177 M/S. METAL CRAFT & ORS. ,A s.17(iii)(b). Reference is to \"produce\".", "start_char": 1377, "end_char": 1595, "num_sentences": 3, "doc_similarity": 0.0, "avg_similarity": 0.1356, "role": "Statute", "confidence": 0.9749470353126526, "same_role_chunk_ids": ["supreme_court_judgements_2008_2008_10_176_189_en_4", "supreme_court_judgements_2008_2008_10_176_189_en_25", "supreme_court_judgements_2008_2008_10_176_189_en_26", "supreme_court_judgements_2008_2008_10_176_189_en_27", "supreme_court_judgements_2008_2008_10_176_189_en_28", "supreme_court_judgements_2008_2008_10_176_189_en_29", "supreme_court_judgements_2008_2008_10_176_189_en_31", "supreme_court_judgements_2008_2008_10_176_189_en_38"]}
